title: FRIDAY - Lamar Jackson out vs Steelers 2020
itunes:title: FRIDAY - Lamar Jackson out vs Steelers 2020
description:
The Ravens-Steelers game already postponed until Sunday, now Baltimore will be without Lamar Jackson as he tests positive for COVID-19 (0:09). Meanwhile, in Arizona (0:39) Larry Fitzgerald testing positive as well as he'll miss Sunday's game against the Patriots. The Bears still figuring out their QB situation (1:11) while Thanksgiving day saw Washington defeat Dallas (1:41) as Mike McCarthy calls a controversial fake punt that didn't work out as planned (2:40). The early game (3:24) saw Deshaun Watson throw 4 TD passes as the seat continues to get hotter for Lions head coach Matt Patricia (3:47)
